flowchart LR
  A[ESP32 Lead I ECG Sensor] --> B[Streaming Window Buffer]
  B --> C[Preprocessing: resample, baseline removal, bandpass, wavelet, normalize]
  C --> D[4-Block 1D CNN Frontend]
  D --> E[6-Layer Transformer Encoder, 8 Heads, 256 Dim]
  E --> F[Embedding]
  E --> G[Signal Quality Index Head]
  F --> H[Deep SVDD]
  F --> I[Mahalanobis Scorer]
  H --> J[Anomaly Score]
  I --> J
  J --> K[OMI Suspicion Score]
  G --> L[signal_quality and noise_score]
  K --> M[Real-Time JSON Output]
  L --> M
